.TH "TODOPRO GOALS" "1" "2026-02-27" "1.0.0" "todopro goals Manual"
.SH NAME
todopro\-goals \- Focus goals and progress tracking
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B todopro goals
[OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
Focus goals and progress tracking
.SH COMMANDS
.PP
\fBshow-goals\fP
  Show current goals and progress.
  See \fBtodopro goals-show-goals(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBshow-goals\fP command.
.PP
\fBshow\fP
  Show current goals and progress.
  See \fBtodopro goals-show(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBshow\fP command.
.PP
\fBset\fP
  Set a focus goal.
  See \fBtodopro goals-set(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBset\fP command.
.PP
\fBlist\fP
  List all configured goals.
  See \fBtodopro goals-list(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBlist\fP command.
.PP
\fBreset\fP
  Reset goals to defaults.
  See \fBtodopro goals-reset(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBreset\fP command.
